{"tid":863152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離個兩個港女 會唔會太造作","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:50:51.000Z","uid":201220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f27393c46e4460e2e6ee138ec88599311372bc27","tid":863152,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"一個人食野 隔離枱有兩個女 都係20幾<br />\n係到講返工啊 咩公司咁<br />\n個問題係 點解要一句中一句英<br />\n如果真係想練 就講哂英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時講完I don&rsquo;t know why they always skip dinner<br />\n另外個個接又話其實我都唔明點解佢地要skip dinner囉<br />\n<br />\n之後A講完一句英文 B又用英文接 接到一半 係到her her...講唔出表達唔到 又講返中文：佢呢 blablabla....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n明明聽到佢地又要勁地道咁講潮語<br />\n於是一直係咁一句中一句英咁 真係好咩 講到我痛都頭埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c2ec82ac6c992a5aac925260105737b142c308","tid":863152,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"樓主應該即時除褲屌撚柒死兩條港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8791c3de84f9a45585dfa9c30da4183f2be2dbd","tid":863152,"uid":74509,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"咁你應該埋單走人，大大聲講:<br />\nexcuse me, 埋bill please。<br />\n俾完錢記得講keep the 找續。<br />\n跟住佢地應該會望過黎，到時你記得想我佢地微笑。"},{"pid":"d5605ba094acc33be22889d7db5828c5f573b9a0","tid":863152,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/194902_96d184227020a104d03461517a8b7f38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F194902_96d184227020a104